Show HN: ChatWebpage – The GPT-powered way to get answers from any webpage
text:
Hey everyone!

I'm excited to share a project I've been working on called ChatWebpage -- it's a website that lets you chat with any webpage using AI.

All you have to do is enter the URL and your question, and the AI will give you a response. It's a great way to quickly get the information you need without having to sift through a lot of text.

I built ChatWebpage because I wanted to create a tool that could make the web more accessible and efficient for everyone. I think it's a really cool way to interact with websites, and I hope you'll find it useful too.

So if you're interested in the latest AI technology, head over to ChatWebpage.com and give it a try! And if you have any feedback or ideas for how I can improve the site, please don't hesitate to reach out.

Thanks for checking it out, and happy chatting!
